I want to like this one, I really do. However, it just never really coalesced into anything for me. The anomalous properties of the slide itself seem to be unrelated to the extra dimension, unless I missed something. Nothing really comes out of the exploration log, and the dado-like  sign just seems to contradict the tone of the rest of the SCP. The ending list of recovered materials didn't seem to make anything more clear, and I'm unsure what emotion the SCP overall wants me to feel.

